      "span_text": "In any event, the presence of an alternative gp130 with distinct responsiveness to various members of this cytokine family suggests additional means whereby specificity can be imparted in the actions of distinct cytokines using the same signal transduction pathway, as sequences present in the ␤ subunits determine the activation of specific substrates"
